{"tid":1805314,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"去唔去澳洲讀OT好？","createTime":"2019-12-31T14:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T12:35:15.000Z","uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"38ec48b66a58e6da03a925262f1a2f1bb4f21387","tid":1805314,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T14:33:57.000Z","msg":"小弟今年asso 社科 文科仔 2019 DSE 19 分 英文lv3 asso讀得唔算辛苦 但真係好多人爭住入大學 2年之後出黎乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n父母深藍 見到中大 Poly 咁多汽油彈之後嚇親想掟我去澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁佢哋想我讀專業資格 我讀asso 讀到好頹 我覺得我入得番八大 但真心乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋我想移民 所以諗緊讀唔讀OT好 但如果要讀foundation 到時24歲先畢業 頌要係成功畢到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到底去唔去好 但唔去我驚我呢世都移唔到民 除左馬來西亞同台灣<br />\n<br />\n身邊個個都話去，但我不嬲好怕分離 雖然可以FaceTime 但我覺得好辛苦 自己一個去陌生環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又好怕grad 唔到要defer 有冇人話我知去唔去好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6f58f4f8dac70464499283a826b51a11db95d0","tid":1805314,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"有無諗過東華ot"},{"pid":"843ed96976271b43e9307a16cbcc636c22a4477c","tid":1805314,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e6f58f4f8dac70464499283a826b51a11db95d0","tid":1805314,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"有無諗過東華ot"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"唔夠分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" clas